UINT32  parm5,
UINT32  parm6,
UINT32  parm7
)  [static]
 

Requests a MAPI extension command to be executed (acceptance of the request is up to APOXI audio priority management).

Parameters:
command_code identifies the kind of command to be executed, see enum CommandCodeType
parm1..6 MAPI parameters, cast to UINT32
parm7 address of priority info struct (PriorityInfoType*) for commands that need priority
Returns:
outcome of the request to APOXI audio priority management, and MAPI return value (meaningful only if the command was actually executed), see enum RequestOutcomeType
